==English==

===Adjective===
{{en-adj-er-y|wear|y}}

# A feeling of being mentally fatigued.
#:''A '''weary''' traveller knocked at the door.''
# [[expressive]] of [[fatigue]].
#:''He gave me a '''weary''' smile.''

